title: Canada's parliament sings new gender-neutral national anthem
text:
Canada's parliament sings new gender-neutral national anthem 3:36am IST - 01:08 
Canadian members of parliament sang the new, gender-neutral lyrics to their national anthem on Wednesday just hours after the change was officially enshrined in law. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
